text: Filipe Jacinto Nyusi (, born 9 February 1959), also spelled Nyussi, is a Mozambican politician. He serves as the fourth President of Mozambique, in office since 2015. ==References== ==Other websites== * Candidate Profile published by FRELIMO Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of Mozambique Category:Current national leaders
title: Filipe Nyusi
